            <title>[CASSANDRA-2241] BRAF read can loop infinitely instead of detecting EOF</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2241</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
